name: xwebgl.js
tagline: A simple WEBGL wrapper for HTML
body:
### Welcome to xwebgl.js.

xwebgl.js is a simple, object-oriented wrapper API for WebGL.

### Features
xwebgl.js is a WebGL/HTML5 based wrapper for web application design, allowing both high-level and low-level programming with high performances.
